snippet.title: CastleStorm Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The clouds of war have arrived in CastleStorm, a super genre mashup of physics based destruction meets tower defense brawler.

Now available for download on PC, consoles, and mobile platforms!

http://www.castlestormgame.com/

CastleStorm on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/241410/ 

CastleStorm on PlayStation: https://store.playstation.com/#!/en-us/search/q=castlestorm 

CastleStorm on Xbox One: https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/search/result.aspx?q=CastleStorm&form=apps&search= 

CastleStorm on Wii U: http://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/mDzzJc-CN4wbC4WQtFFdAIRTkjl9DmUH 

CastleStorm on iOS: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/castlestorm-free-to-siege/id726232588?mt=8 

CastleStorm on Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.zenstudios.castlestorm&hl=en 

CastleStorm on Amazon: https://www.amazon.com/Zen-Studios-CastleStorm-Free-Siege/dp/B00JXD0YXI/ref=sr_1_1?s=mobile-apps&ie=UTF8&qid=1478801214&sr=1-1&keywords=castlestorm 

CastleStorm on Rift: https://www.oculus.com/experiences/rift/899545263499753/ 

CastleStorm on Gear VR: https://www.oculus.com/experiences/gear-vr/1059251330800683/
